{"tid":2377473,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好想知佢係咪鐘意我","createTime":"2021-01-23T15:55:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T05:06:14.000Z","uid":179792,"like":2,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"737e8732e170d883e73e3d6ce07d750ea9ba2122","tid":2377473,"uid":179792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T15:55:00.000Z","msg":"話說我最近鐘意咗個女同事，成日都掛住佢，但佢好似成日都唔理我咁<br />\n<br />\n之前對佢都無感覺，因為大家工作上都無咩交流，點知之前佢無啦啦約我去睇戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁個時無feel，又對套戲無興趣咪拒絕咗佢，之後大家fd咗間唔中會同佢吹水。<br />\n返工有時一班同事一齊食飯佢係咁話要同我兩個人坐又話我點好，係咁flirt我，個時仲心諗係咪想玩我。但之後大家吹水吹得多咗佢又對我幾好，唔知幾時開始我就對佢有啲feel。咁想約佢，點知佢又唔得閒，有時WhatsApp/Signal搵佢吹水，但佢又唔覆，或者勁耐先覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但返工有時大家同lift，佢又會好主動咁同我打招呼，有次明明部lift又唔係無位，但佢行過黎企我隔離同我講完早晨仲挨埋落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想知佢究竟係咪鐘意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定玩我。<br />\n<br />\n自問樣唔差，算高大，有人話靚仔，有人話正常樣，對人又唔差，啲同事都話我親善大使，間唔中啲fd都話介紹啲女比我，但又無咩興趣，啲fd成日叫我去做健身教練，大把女搵我。<br />\n<br />\n知你有上連登但唔知你有冇睇到我呢個post，雖然你又矮又細粒又無波，但你對我好好又幾可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果你係鐘意嘅就同我講，雖然我話叫你介紹啲女女比我識，但你真係介紹啲女女比我識，我對佢地唔會有興趣架啦，因為我個心只能有你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我之前對你無feel但而家有，仲無時無刻都諗住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb3f7684355596da04319c7bbecad1cd65d1271","tid":2377473,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T15:57:41.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"135adcc7cd6f0bfd378180812c895bdb9da8ba6b","tid":2377473,"uid":218575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T15:59:52.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"3640d743f84870f0d0afa5603e5df186c894fea5","tid":2377473,"uid":9392,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:12:32.000Z","msg":"知你靚仔喇屌你老母臭西"},{"pid":"4077cffb0a0efeba1fbaa9f42ac006900f8b993a","tid":2377473,"uid":179792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:12:47.000Z","msg":"係啲咩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但如果真係中意我無理由搵佢吹水都唔點覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad2cc51eb6af18b540bf674f193352a25d94fd5","tid":2377473,"uid":179792,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3640d743f84870f0d0afa5603e5df186c894fea5","tid":2377473,"uid":9392,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:12:32.000Z","msg":"知你靚仔喇屌你老母臭西"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:13:20.000Z","msg":"我老母個西唔臭，但我知你把口又賤又臭"},{"pid":"1db0efc3e0c780af998e684d1db27e1cb8b83623","tid":2377473,"uid":165341,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:13:58.000Z","msg":"咪撚咁多啦痴漢"},{"pid":"f192fc349750369f08e74c35e3b11ffff3fec126","tid":2377473,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bad2cc51eb6af18b540bf674f193352a25d94fd5","tid":2377473,"uid":179792,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3640d743f84870f0d0afa5603e5df186c894fea5","tid":2377473,"uid":9392,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:12:32.000Z","msg":"知你靚仔喇屌你老母臭西"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:13:20.000Z","msg":"我老母個西唔臭，但我知你把口又賤又臭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:14:02.000Z","msg":"哈哈 爽"},{"pid":"48b1aff04616cb945ac1381f02c077273128e93a","tid":2377473,"uid":9392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:14:18.000Z","msg":"你老母比狗屌"},{"pid":"9945da9e0ede7b8040e134454a14c3e6f3abca22","tid":2377473,"uid":9392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T16:14:30.000Z","msg":"全家仆街死"},{"pid":"62077b5ee86c22e7d01a8df46a37bea1be3f0d3b","tid":2377473,"uid":218575,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"